instructions:
Stir soup until smooth. Beat in eggs and pepper.
Heat butter in skillet. Add egg mixture. Cook until set but still very moist, stirring lightly. Sprinkle with parsley.
title: Classic Campbelled Eggs
ingredients: 1 (10.75 ounce) can Campbell's® Condensed Cream of Celery Soup or Campbell's® Condensed 98% Fat Free Cream of Celery Soup
